snippet.title: Super Metroid Digital Cube 100% TAS in 00:06
snippet.description:
TAS of one of the newest super metroid hacks from Cloud12
15:39 until last room escape, 00:06 ingame time^^ 
100% is 5 Energy cells,5 Power Bombs, 5 Super missiles, 5 Missiles Pack and every items (what represent 47% of the original Super Metroid).
This hack is a minihack made for a contest, check it out here in minihack submissions:
http://themetroid.proboards.com/index.cgi?board=contests
Check this out and take a look at Super Metroid Advent and Super Metroid Dark Plague, the minihacks of the contest :)
